cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as image recognition and image importance prediction, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The use of neural networks and deep learning techniques also suggests a possible fit under cs.MM (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of organizing and curating photo albums. The use of LSTM-based sequence level event recognizer suggests a possible fit under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper involves a hybrid system consisting of multiple components, which could potentially fit under cs.LG (Learning).
